        <h2 class="dark-gray">How it all started</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="passion-details">
        <p class="light-gray">
          NicholsMD of Greenwich was founded by Dr. Kim Nichols, a board-certified dermatologist with a vision to
          redefine personalized skincare. Inspired by her passion for helping clients achieve radiant, healthy skin, Dr.
          Nichols opened her boutique dermatology practice to deliver cutting-edge treatments and expert care in a
          welcoming environment. And what began as a small, dedicated team has grown into one of the most trusted
          practices in cosmetic dermatology, offering a wide range of services tailored to individual needs.<br>
          <br>
